topic.p:
Raw coroutine is an expression which looks like:

    $coroutine{ ... }

This expression returns system::Coroutine^.

Coroutine function (including lambda expressions) is written in these forms:

    func ... : void
    $NAME {
        ...
    }

or

    func ... : Something
    $NAME {
        ...
    }

or

    func ... : Something
    ${
        ...
    }
